\newlabel{fig:coefplot}{{3}{18}{Coefficient forest plot. Left: Tier 1 cross-sectional OLS, 2020 snapshot, with GDP control. Right: Tier 2 two-way fixed-effects panel, 2013--2022, country and year FE, GDP control, country-clustered standard errors. The composite and apostasy are pinned to the top of each panel; other GRI sub-items appear below for context. GDP shown in italic grey as a control. Coefficients with $95\%$ confidence intervals}{figure.caption.4}{}}
