\newlabel{fig:mundlak}{{4}{19}{Mundlak correlated random-effects decomposition, Tier 4. Left panel: within-country effect for each predictor. Right panel: between-country effect. The composite row is highlighted. The between/within ratio in the centre is $|\beta _2 / \beta _1|$ for the composite}{figure.caption.5}{}}
